      "review_summary": "The PR adds a default-off `streaming.progress.persistProgress` config flag, freezes progress lines in the shared compositor, prepends them to Telegram final answers, refreshes generated channel metadata, and adds unit coverage plus a Telegram UI hint.\n\nPR surface: Source +95, Tests +189, Generated 0. Total +284 across 9 files.\n\nReproducibility: not applicable. as a user bug report. The remaining blocker is source-reproducible from the PR diff: the shared schema accepts `persistProgress`, but only Telegram final delivery consumes frozen progress text.",
